Task executed and verified: the MCP server in this repo starts via `.\mvnw.cmd -q -f pulsar-agentic\pom.xml org.codehaus.mojo:exec-maven-plugin:3.6.1:java -Dexec.mainClass=ai.platon.pulsar.agentic.mcp.server.Browser4MCPServerRunnerKt`, not via the packaged `Browser4.jar`. It initialized successfully, launched Chrome, and registered 121 MCP tools; then it exited cleanly once STDIO closed, which is expected unless an MCP client keeps stdin open.

I appended the result and lessons learned to `coworker\tasks\300logs\2026\03\08\MEMORY.20260308.md`, and the monthly memory already contained the prior-day rollup so no monthly append was needed.


